roximal subiculum at late intervals. Thus, concomitant up-regulation of subunit \&\#x3B3;2, \&\#x3B1;1 and \&\#x3B1;4 mRNAs (and loss in \&\#x3B4;-subunits) ultimately indicates significant rearrangement of GABAA receptor composition after KA-induced seizures.},
